  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Aid to the Victims of Nyiragongo volcano in Goma</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Middle of May 2021 thousand of families in the Democratic Republic of Congo  Goma and its surrounding areas has left hundreds of displaced and panic-stricken citizens. Due to the Nyiragongo volcanic eruption and earthquakes, it has led to blocked evacuation roads and hundreds of deaths. Multiple people have been displaced ,no access to food or shelter. Children Hope Forever has organised itself to providing emergency fresh food, water, tarp shelters, blankets for 500 displaced  families.</narrative>
  </description>
